00:14:40.840 --> 00:14:44.559
but you can make use of your preferred model provider

00:14:44.559 --> 00:14:47.679
and models directly alongside the code that you're working on.

00:14:49.760 --> 00:14:52.479
So what we're trying to say here is that Positron

00:14:52.479 --> 00:14:55.000
