00:25:15.280 --> 00:25:17.439
will Positron come at an added cost?

00:25:17.439 --> 00:25:19.719
Positron is free on desktop, right?

00:25:19.719 --> 00:25:22.079
So you could just download and try that today.

00:25:22.079 --> 00:25:23.920
